org.apache.hadoop.hive.accumulo.serde

Class CompositeAccumuloRowIdFactory<T extends AccumuloCompositeRowId>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hive.accumulo.serde.DefaultAccumuloRowIdFactory
      • org.apache.hadoop.hive.accumulo.serde.CompositeAccumuloRowIdFactory<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    AccumuloRowIdFactory

    public class CompositeAccumuloRowIdFactory<T extends AccumuloCompositeRowId>
extends DefaultAccumuloRowIdFactory
    AccumuloRowIdFactory designed for injection of the AccumuloCompositeRowId to be used to generate the Accumulo rowId. Allows for custom AccumuloCompositeRowIds to be specified without overriding the entire ObjectInspector for the Hive row.
